This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the use of neural networks for translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with the use of AI for language translation. The paper also mentions the use of distributed representations, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the use of parallel corpora, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as parallel corpora are often used in image captioning tasks.
